<div class="container">
        <h1>Guide: Dividend Investing for Beginners (2026)</h1>
        <p class="intro">Building a passive income portfolio doesn't have to be complicated. Learn the mechanics of dividend investing, how to evaluate safe yields, and why compound interest is your greatest asset.</p>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
